M. Rosier pass,to J. Thomas for 48 yds for a TD, (M. Badgley KICK)

videos.description: Eric Dungey's is picked off by Hurricane's DL Demetrius Jackson who is immediately stripped by Dungey.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Syracuse QB steals ball back after his interception) 2017/10/21

videos.headline: Syracuse QB steals ball back after his interception

videos.description: Eric Dungey's pass is intercepted by Michael Jackson and he and his teammates celebrate with the turnover chain on the sidelines.
videos.headline: Jackson's pick nets him Miami's turnover chain

videos.description: Malik Rosier completes to Christopher Herndon IV for a 10-yard touchdown to extend the Hurricanes' lead.
videos.headline: Rosier finds Johnson in the end zone

videos.description: Jaquan Johnson picks off Eric Dungey on the Miami 38-yard line and the Hurricanes celebrate again with the turnover chain.
videos.headline: Miami wears the turnover chain again after Dungey throws his 3rd pick

videos.description: Miami WR Ahmmon Richards catches a pass and hurdles a Syracuse defender before being brought down for a 21-yard gain.
videos.headline: Miami's Richards hurdles over defender

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Miami's Richards hurdles over defender) 2017/10/21 ESHEET

videos.description: Syracuse head coach Dino Babers is looking to come out strong in the second half and find big runs after trailing Miami 13-3.
videos.headline: Babers: 'Excited about what we can do in the second half'

videos.description: Moe Neal rushes for 15 yards into the end zone to close the gap on Miami.
videos.headline: Neal responds with an Orange TD

videos.description: Malik Rosier throws a deep ball to Jeff Thomas for a 48-yard touchdown to extend the Hurricanes' lead.
videos.headline: Rosier connects with Thomas for 48-yard TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rosier connects with Thomas for 48-yard TD) 2017/10/21

videos.description: Syracuse QB Eric Dungey rushes for a big gain while hitting a Miami defender with a karate-like move.
videos.headline: Dungey hits the defender with a flying knee

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dungey hits the defender with a flying knee) 2017/10/21

videos.description: Travis Homer runs for a 33-yard touchdown to extend the Hurricanes' lead.
videos.headline: Homer rushes 33 yards to the house
